{"tid":1380013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"728後 [推到全人類有豬嘴] 百幾蚊就100%防! 豬嘴護目鏡攻略(應對對方升級催淚彈)!!","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:00:26.000Z","uid":105976,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2516598867bd6669fee56df64e19be88ea7be073","tid":1380013,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:10:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">經過兄弟裝修實測<br />\n連$100既3200+3311k  戴得好 近距裝修都絕對防禦</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n728後 發現濃度有所提升 plan1 同 2C plan可能唔夠做  <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">千奇唔好濕水 濕水filter會失效</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">濃度太高filter時限都會減少</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全防具spreadsheet (建議用pc睇)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c45462a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n無論和平定勇武 裝修都一定會被放煙<br />\n如果一食煙就退 前面既工友就冇人支援<br />\n所以保護自已=保護他人 無論果次裝修講到明好安全<br />\n都一定要帶齊安全裝備<br />\n<br />\n首先 對付既係有機氣體+大量結晶體 防塵果D口罩/外科口罩係冇用<br />\n所以濾罐能力要 防有機氣體 + P100級既濾棉 (100%防顆粒)<br />\n仲要配密氣式護目鏡 (泳鏡or 氣密式鏡 一定要non-vented!!!)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">泳鏡其實都有好細既孔  搵到就用玻璃膠封住</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">護目鏡推呢隻  火場用 完全氣密</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07CQFYTCT/ref=ox_sc_act_image_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07CQFYTCT%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_image_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=93a420b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07CQFYTCT/ref=ox_sc_act_image_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住防具係保護自已 唔會犯法, 每個人都有更加唔洗驚俾人針對<br />\n<br />\n濾罐時效有200小時 (戴住呼吸先計)   (濃度太高會加速老化)<br />\n用完用密實袋包好佢 下次再用 有效期大約半年<br />\n<br />\n懶人包: (以下豬嘴+濾罐濾棉都係3M牌子, 每一隻plan都100%防)<br />\n1. 3200豬嘴 + 3311k濾罐 (防有機氣體+防晶體) (實測100%防 戴住長期跑會有點呼吸不順)<br />\n一套大約140蚊<br />\n任何一間五金鋪入去問佢 90%都有 <br />\n<br />\n2. (A)<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">6200/6500/7500豬嘴+ 60926濾罐</span></strong> (防有機氣體+ 100%防晶體) (難買, 實測100%防)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">60921 60923 60925 69028</span> 都同樣有效 <br />\n<br />\n豬嘴6200 6500 7500 5金鋪都會搵到 真係冇先上網買 因為運過黎都要成星期 (雖然網購平d)<br />\n<br />\n602926購買連結: 1對22usd<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/3M-Cartridge-60926-Respiratory-Protection/dp/B009POHLRC/ref=sr_1_2_sspa?crid=263BB1V1XWE2J&amp;keywords=3m+6006+cartridge&amp;qid=1564048054&amp;s=gateway&amp;sprefix=3M+6006%2Caps%2C835&amp;sr=8-2-spons&amp;psc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F3M-Cartridge-60926-Respiratory-Protection%2Fdp%2FB009POHLRC%2Fref%3Dsr_1_2_sspa%3Fcrid%3D263BB1V1XWE2J%26keywords%3D3m%2B6006%2Bcartridge%26qid%3D1564048054%26s%3Dgateway%26sprefix%3D3M%2B6006%252Caps%252C835%26sr%3D8-2-spons%26psc%3D1&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=acbe1712\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/3M-Cartridge-60926-Respiratory-Protection/dp/B009POHLRC/ref=sr_1_2_sspa?crid=263BB1V1XWE2J&amp;keywords=3m+6006+cartridge&amp;qid=1564048054&amp;s=gateway&amp;sprefix=3M+6006%2Caps%2C835&amp;sr=8-2-spons&amp;psc=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(B) <span style=\"color: red;\">6200/6500/7500豬嘴 + 6006濾罐 + 502 外蓋 + 2091濾棉</span> (100%防晶體) (實測100%防)<br />\n瀘罐6006都係5金鋪買就有 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2091  2096   2097     2291 2296  2297  都一樣有效!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n502外蓋購買連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Compatible-Respirator-Prefilters-Prefilter-Adaptor/dp/B07Q87NPN3/ref=sr_1_4?keywords=3m+502&amp;qid=1564048174&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCompatible-Respirator-Prefilters-Prefilter-Adaptor%2Fdp%2FB07Q87NPN3%2Fref%3Dsr_1_4%3Fkeywords%3D3m%2B502%26qid%3D1564048174%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-4&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=232ed8d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Compatible-Respirator-Prefilters-Prefilter-Adaptor/dp/B07Q87NPN3/ref=sr_1_4?keywords=3m+502&amp;qid=1564048174&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4</a><br />\n<br />\n2901濾棉 1對7usd<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/3M-Filter-2091P100-2-Bag/dp/B001D1JCK4/ref=sr_1_12?keywords=3m+2901+filter&amp;qid=1564048476&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F3M-Filter-2091P100-2-Bag%2Fdp%2FB001D1JCK4%2Fref%3Dsr_1_12%3Fkeywords%3D3m%2B2901%2Bfilter%26qid%3D1564048476%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-12&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=2f0f6686\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/3M-Filter-2091P100-2-Bag/dp/B001D1JCK4/ref=sr_1_12?keywords=3m+2901+filter&amp;qid=1564048476&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-12</a><br />\n<br />\n(C) <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">6200/6500/7500豬嘴 + 2097濾棉</span></strong> (呢隻濾棉可以防埋有機氣體+顆粒) 2207棉係新版 一樣得     <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(對家升級左催淚彈, 濃度太高呢個plan可能唔夠做)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2097連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/3M-Particulate-Filter-Organic-Filters/dp/B079X5C3QP/ref=sr_1_2?keywords=3m+2907&amp;qid=1564048531&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-Organic-Filters%2Fdp%2FB079X5C3QP%2Fref%3Dsr_1_2%3Fkeywords%3D3m%2B2907%26qid%3D1564048531%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-2&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=9fa6e8c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/3M-Particulate-Filter-Organic-Filters/dp/B079X5C3QP/ref=sr_1_2?keywords=3m+2907&amp;qid=1564048531&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n60926濾罐難買 AMAZON有, 可以俾多少少錢特快運 都平過HK五金鋪<br />\n要快就記得選特快運送mode<br />\n<br />\n6200/6500/7500 都係雙濾罐設計 用既濾罐都一樣 愈高級愈戴得舒服/愈氣密/愈貴 <br />\n<br />\n上場之前記得測試氣密度<br />\n用手輕按住口罩前方既換氣蓋<br />\n之後用少少力吹氣 如果冇空氣由豬嘴貼住面部既gap位到漏走 你豬嘴就成功氣密左<br />\n<br />\n至於點解琴晚大家覺得豬嘴有d唔夠頂 仲研究緊 有更新會即刻俾大家知  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最新催淚彈成份表<br />\n化學jj請幫手睇<br />\n80%都係cs gas (同其他一樣)<br />\n有冇邊d奇怪成份<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDK0ti7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDK0ti7.png&h=06e27d8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01ffe94f988160daef3fb588f30e58d38a87c683","tid":1380013,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDr.Incognito.HK%2F&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=628c4fd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打無名博士的fb   有詳盡又易明既豬嘴 護目鏡圖解<br />\n非常建議都去睇"},{"pid":"2deadbd93421bbfd949fa59234d88b241d31076b","tid":1380013,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83d7fc1f5e02a5b99671db6d545ca3b202922f9","tid":1380013,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86e71d1d2b58345a3a9a525830677d93fb5c8dc","tid":1380013,"uid":65343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"amazon買最快幾時有"},{"pid":"550c511fdb8fff785f1c9038760b59781a23a3ac","tid":1380013,"uid":41460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"推<br /